                <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Deal closes at 4 PM. Invoice exists in accounting by 4:15 PM. One source of truth, updated as events happen.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Complete Audit Trail</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Every data movement recorded. Who updated what. When it changed. Why it moved. Compliance and debugging become straightforward.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Time Freed for Revenue Work</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-600">The person whose job was syncing systems? That 10-15 hours per week is now available for core business work.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Flexible Engagement</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Build + Maintain or Build + Operate models—we adapt to how you work and what you need.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Who This Is For -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12">
            Who This Is For
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Businesses Using 3+ Systems</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-600">CRM, accounting, project management, and other platforms that should talk to each other</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <div>
